htw.vs1.filesystem.Network.Discovery

Class FileSystemServer

  • java.lang.Object
    • htw.vs1.filesystem.Network.Discovery.FileSystemServer

  • public class FileSystemServer
extends java.lang.Object
    A FileSystemServer represents a remote server running a file system instance. This class contains all necessary information to connect with this server. Host and Port together is unique for a FileSystemServer instance. Created by Felix on 22.09.2015.
